title: Poster, 1993-53-116, 1990
inscribed: Other text: "Nelson Mandela was released from prison February 11th, 1990. Nearly one year later 3,000 political prisoner remains in apartheid's jails. These are just some of their names. [Extensive list of names]" Imprinted on bottom: "To Help Free South Africa's Political Prisoners contact The Africa Fund..."
creditline: Gift of Steven Heller and Karrie Jacobs
